{"Q0":"I started to see a pattern of the different pairs. The key was the pairing. I used color and pattern to try and figure which one stood out or was best within that pairing.

When they were a bit more similar as far as how much pattern or color they had, I went with the one that had the most or at least seemed to have the most of both os those. 

There were times when the same pairing showed up twice in a row but they were reversed, left side was now on the right side. They were only a few of those and they were not that common.

I also thought that when one of them did not have that much color and the other one did, the one with the least amount of color was the "right" one. Not a lot of these either but I thought there was a pattern.

The pairing also repeated at times but far apart within each  round and even farther apart between rounds. Almost like measuring if we had learned the patter or patterns."}
